::Zardus::

Zardus shakes his head. "Not at all. Stay as much as you like."

He stands up. "I'll keep in mind Darkfate's feelings toward the Infecticons when dealing with them."

He walks out of the room, the door closing behind him. The room, as well as the ship, were all monitoring Orchestra, of course.
